+| 🔔 | `<text class="fa fa-bell"></text>` |
+| ✏️ | `<text class="fa fa-pen"></text>` |
+| 📸 | `<text class="fa fa-camera"></text>` |
+| 🔍 | `<text class="fa fa-search"></text>` |
